\begin_layout Section
Def.
 Complete residue system
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
A complete residue system S mod n is a set of integers s.t.
 every integer is congruent to a unique member of S.
 E.g.
 
\begin_inset Formula $S=\left\{ 1,2,\ldots,10\right\} $
\end_inset

 is a complete residue system mod 
\begin_inset Formula $10.$
\end_inset

 
\end_layout

